column2: select * from OPENQUERY ([#.#], #' #) as case_ids from cancer_study cs inner join sample_list sl on sl.CANCER_STUDY_ID = cs.CANCER_STUDY_ID join sample_list_list sll on sl.list_id = sll.list_id join sample s on s.internal_id = sll.sample_id where cs.cancer_study_identifier = #gbm_tcga# and s1.stable_id = #gbm_tcga_all# group by sl.stable_id, sl.cancer_study_id order by #, #') a
